      • getMissing

        public long getMissing()
        The number of resources which have no value for the corresponding field. Use case: in a product search where a term facet is requested for a color attribute, it would represent the amount of variants with no color associated.
        Returns:
        amount of resources missing a value for the faceted field.

      • getTotal

        The number of resources matching some term in the facet.
        Returns:
